data.description: Welcome to this charming residence nestled in a sought-after golf course community, where comfort and leisure unite. High ceilings throughout the main level create an elegant and spacious ambiance, while gleaming hardwood floors add warmth and character. The kitchen is a standout feature, with granite countertops and an island that serves as a breakfast bar, offering both style and functionality. This home boasts two primary bedrooms, providing flexibility and convenience for residents or guests. Enjoy the outdoors on the screened in porch while staying protected from the elements. The beautiful landscaping, which the HOA maintains, enhances the curb appeal and overall charm. The neighborhood offers access to a pool and tennis courts, providing ample opportunities for recreation. Enjoy the convenience of living in a great location, with easy access to Raleigh and all the amenities and entertainment options it has to offer.  *Home will be professionally measured and photographed
